宫崎英高将不再执导未来FromSoftware魂类游戏https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/future-fromsoftware-soulslike-games-wont-be-directed-by-hidetaka-miyazaki-3593151?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=future-fromsoftware-soulslike-宫崎英高导演的游戏Ali ShutlerMon, 26 Feb 2024 16:51:58 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS5xbox series x/shttps://www.nme.com/?p=3593151 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑暗之魂重制版（来源：Bandai Namco）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>宫崎骏还称赞《黑暗之魂》启发了《埃尔登指环》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/future-fromsoftware-soulslike-games-wont-be-directed-by-hidetaka-miyazaki-3593151">宫崎英高执导的《Future FromSoftware》灵魂类游戏将</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑暗之魂重制版（来源：Bandai Namco）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>宫崎英高表示，他“很有可能”不会参与未来的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a>游戏《魂》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/ten-years-on-dark-souls-is-still-corralling-us-through-its-hostile-world-3052179">十年过去了，《黑暗之魂》仍然将我们困在充满敌意的世界中</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">《Elden Ring》</a></em>和《<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dark-souls"><em>黑暗之魂》</em></a>之间，FromSoftware 已成为“类魂”游戏的首选工作室，常任导演宫崎骏将类魂类游戏定义为“那些更注重近战战斗和感官体验的黑暗奇幻第三人称动作游戏”的成就。”他知道自己在说什么，几乎执导了所有<em>《埃尔登指环》</em>和<em>《黑暗之魂》</em>的作品。</p><p> 2014 年的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dark-souls-2">《黑暗之魂 2》</a></em>是个例外。该作品由宫崎骏担任监督，涩谷智博和谷村唯担任导演。</p><p>在<em><a href="https://nordic.ign.com/elden-ring/79128/feature/two-years-after-elden-ring-miyazaki-trusts-the-players-to-figure-it-all-out" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IGN</a></em>的一次新采访中，宫崎骏证实他不会参与任何未来的灵魂类游戏。 “我认为我们很可能会看到新的董事继续前进。我认为如果我们这样做，我想放弃监督角色，并给予他们对这些项目的全面指导和完全控制。我认为这确实是他们在这种环境和新项目中蓬勃发展的最佳方式和最简单的方式，”他解释道。</p><p> “我认为主管的角色对我来说只是我不习惯的，而且可能不太适合，”他补充道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《黑暗之魂：重制版》- 发布预告片 | PS4" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Woe0PYZPxRw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>随着<em>《黑暗之魂 2》</em>聘请了新导演，FromSoftware“能够拥有不同的动力、不同的想法，并建立我们原本不可能拥有的不同的联系。如果没有<em>《黑暗之魂 2》，</em>我们真的无法判断这个系列会如何或是否会继续下去，”他补充道。</p><p>在其他地方，宫崎骏称赞<em>《黑暗之魂 2》</em>让 FromSoftware 走上了最终将他们引向<em>《Elden Ring》</em>的道路，该游戏注重开放世界风格的游戏玩法，而不是线性叙事。</p><p> “关于<em>《黑暗之魂 2》</em> ，我个人实际上认为这对我们来说是一个非常伟大的项目，我认为如果没有它，我们就不会有很多联系和很多想法，这些想法会继续下去并承载该系列的其余部分。”</p><p> <em>《Elden Ring</em> 》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-share-first-look-at-the-shadow-of-the-erdtree-expansion-3590766">大型资料片<em>《Shadow Of The Erdtree》</em>将于 6 月发行，</a>但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-director-wont-rule-out-a-sequel-there-could-well-be-something-in-the-future-3591250">宫崎骏拒绝排除续集的可能性。</a></p><p>在其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/nier"><em>《尼尔》</em></a>导演横尾太郎显然已经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nier-director-teases-follow-up-to-2017s-nier-automata-3593122">开始预告该系列的第三款游戏。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/future-fromsoftware-soulslike-games-wont-be-directed-by-hidetaka-miyazaki-3593151">宫崎英高执导的《Future FromSoftware》灵魂类游戏将</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
